    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1895-08-28T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1895-08-28T00:00:00-05:00" n="115"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d115">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Denby</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Olney</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Peking</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-08-28">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 28, 1895</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Chinese Government has refused to degrade and punish ex-viceroy Szechuan.
                    Pressure should be used to secure punishment.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Denby</hi>
                    </signed>.</closer>
            </div>
        </body>
